# =========================================================
# üß† Full-Stack Project .gitignore (React + Node + Express + MongoDB + pnpm + TypeScript + Mongoose + Tailwind CSS)
# =========================================================
# üìå Description:
# This .gitignore file is designed for a modern full-stack JavaScript project.
# It covers both frontend (React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS) and backend (Node.js + Express + MongoDB + Mongoose),
# using pnpm as the package manager.
#
# It prevents sensitive data (like .env files), build outputs, caches, dependencies,
# and unnecessary files from being pushed to Git repositories.
# =========================================================


